                            <comment id="17912547" author="JIRAUSER306303" created="Mon, 13 Jan 2025 14:13:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dajac&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dajac&quot;&gt;dajac&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;While working on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-18491&quot; title=&quot;Remove zkClient &amp;amp; maybeUpdateMetadataCache from ReplicaManager&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-18491&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-18491&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I noticed that removing the &lt;tt&gt;controllerEpoch&lt;/tt&gt; has some dependencies with &lt;tt&gt;becomeLeaderOrFollower&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;stopReplicas&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you&apos;re currently occupied and don&apos;t have the bandwidth to handle this ticket, I&apos;d be happy to take it on. Please let me know your thoughts. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17914476" author="ijuma" created="Sun, 19 Jan 2025 17:26:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We should also remove LeaderAndIsrRequest as part of this (or file a separate ticket for that part if it turns out to be complicated) - note that we have to make sure we don&apos;t remove tests that were using zk mechanisms but are still relevant in kraft mode.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17950705" author="chia7712" created="Sat, 10 May 2025 17:30:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dajac&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dajac&quot;&gt;dajac&lt;/a&gt; any updates?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17951449" author="dajac" created="Wed, 14 May 2025 18:02:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=chia7712&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;chia7712&quot;&gt;chia7712&lt;/a&gt; No progress on this one. Feel free to take it if you have bandwidth.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17951534" author="chia7712" created="Thu, 15 May 2025 00:56:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dajac&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dajac&quot;&gt;dajac&lt;/a&gt; thanks for response. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=taijuwu&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;taijuwu&quot;&gt;taijuwu&lt;/a&gt; and I will take over it &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17986782" author="chia7712" created="Sun, 29 Jun 2025 17:21:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There are some follow-up cleanups, but the target function has been removed. Hence, closing this PR as resolved&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
